de.learnlib.algorithms.ttt.base

Class BlockList<I,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.learnlib.algorithms.ttt.base.BlockListElem<I,D>
      • de.learnlib.algorithms.ttt.base.BlockList<I,D>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - input symbol type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<DTNode<I,D>>

    public class BlockList<I,D>
extends BlockListElem<I,D>
implements Iterable<DTNode<I,D>>
    A list for storing blocks (identified by their root DTNodes). The list is implemented as a singly-linked list, and allows O(1) insertion and removal of elements.
    Author:
    Malte Isberner
